   basic input and output of the system  check where the bootable device present like cd,dvd,pendrive 
mbr 
   master boot recorder is the first sector of the  hard disk holds  512 bytes it checks.where boot files are located 
        Primary boot loader info in 1st 446 bytes
         Partition table info in next 64 bytes
        MBR validation check in last 2 bytes.
  
