     kernel execute /sbin/init from intramfs as the first process and pid is 1 
	 While system starting kernel loads all the necessary Kernel Modules and Drives from initrd.img to load system first process systemd pid is 1
init
     /etc/inittab  is the configuration file to decide which run level configured
	  0- shutdown
	  1- single user mode
	  2-- multiuser without nfs
	  3- full multiuser mode without grapic
	  4-unused
	  5-multiuser with grapic
	  6-restart
