now chosing to create primary or extended partition selet e extended
now select sector of new partitoon press enter and for last secort press enter
now give size in GB or MB or TB based on the size of the disk 
now press t to chnage partation id 
we use 8e for linux lvm or to swap id
after changing the id press p print the detail of the partation
now making filesystem formated
